			<label>
Use the Record option to schedule the selected program for recording. Shows that are scheduled for recording will be highlighted red. If you set a show to recurring from this EPG only the current show that you have scheduled to record will be highlighted in red. 

If you would like to cancel the recording simply open this menu while the program is selected and click "Don't Record". If you need to turn off recurring for a show use the Recurring section of USTVnow Plus.

Keep in mind that shows that are set to record within USTVnow Plus itself will not show as scheduled to record in this EPG. If a recording is cancelled in USTVnow Plus it will not show as not being scheduled to record in this EPG if it was originally scheduled from this EPG.

For additional help please visit:
